        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Select_GetSBMRLetterAccountMeters",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve and organize meter and account information related to SBMR (presumably a business-specific term or acronym) letters. It processes data from two tables, "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "SBMRMeter",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "SBMRAccount",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and outputs a consolidated list of account and meter details. The procedure uses a temporary table to manage and manipulate the data before returning the results."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
